sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as Trainer Controller<br/>opendatahub namespace
    participant Plugins as Plugin Framework<br/>(in-process)
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant Scheduler as K8s Scheduler<br/>(CoScheduling/Volcano)
    participant Rank0 as Training Pod (Rank 0)<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant Workers as Training Pods (Workers)<br/>29500/TCP TCP
    participant DCHead as Data Cache Head<br/>gRPC Arrow Flight
    participant DCWorker as Data Cache Workers<br/>gRPC Arrow Flight
    participant Iceberg as Iceberg Metadata<br/>S3/HTTP

    Note over User,Workers: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply TrainJob<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: TrainJob created<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Fetch TrainingRuntime/ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Runtime definition

    Controller->>Plugins: Execute plugin chain
    Note right of Plugins: 1. EnforceMLPolicy (PyTorch/MPI)<br/>2. EnforcePodGroupPolicy (CoSched/Volcano)<br/>3. PodNetwork (NetworkPolicy)<br/>4. ComponentBuilder (JobSet)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create JobSet resource<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PodGroup (if gang scheduling)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap/Secret (if MPI)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+

    K8sAPI->>JobSetCtrl: JobSet created
    JobSetCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create training Pods
    K8sAPI->>Scheduler: Schedule pods (gang scheduling)
    Scheduler-->>K8sAPI: Pods scheduled

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update TrainJob status<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+

    Note over Controller,Workers: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking (RHOAI only)

    loop Every reconciliation cycle
        Controller->>K8sAPI: List pods for TrainJob<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list with IPs
        Controller->>Rank0: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/28080 (No TLS)<br/>NetworkPolicy restricted
        Rank0-->>Controller: Training metrics JSON<br/>(progress, steps, epochs, loss)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Patch TrainJob annotations<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    end

    Note over Rank0,Workers: Flow 3: Distributed PyTorch Training (inter-pod)

    Workers->>Rank0: Connect to master<br/>TCP/29500 (c10d rendezvous)<br/>No encryption, NetworkPolicy: same-job
    Rank0-->>Workers: Rendezvous complete
    Note over Rank0,Workers: NCCL/Gloo collective ops<br/>Dynamic ports, TCP/UDP<br/>No encryption, NetworkPolicy: same-job

    Note over DCHead,Iceberg: Flow 4: Data Cache Distribution (Optional)

    Rank0->>DCHead: get_flight_info<br/>gRPC Arrow Flight (No TLS)
    DCHead->>Iceberg: Read table metadata<br/>HTTP/S3
    Iceberg-->>DCHead: Data file locations
    DCHead->>DCWorker: do_put (distribute data)<br/>gRPC Arrow Flight (No TLS)
    DCWorker-->>DCHead: Acknowledgment
    DCHead-->>Rank0: Flight info (worker assignments)
    Rank0->>DCWorker: do_get (query cached data)<br/>gRPC Arrow Flight (No TLS)
    DCWorker-->>Rank0: Arrow RecordBatch data
